sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as Nguoi dung
    participant FE as Chat UI
    participant API as Chat Stream API
    participant Rasa as Rasa Server
    participant RAG as RAG Service
    participant Emb as Embedding Service
    participant VDB as Vector DB
    participant LLM as LLM
    participant DB as Chat DB

    U->>FE: Gui cau hoi
    FE->>API: Open SSE/WebSocket /chat/stream
    API->>DB: Luu user message
    API->>Rasa: Xu ly nhanh bang Rasa
    Rasa-->>API: intent, confidence, response hoac fallback
    alt Rasa tu tin va co response
        API-->>FE: Stream chunk tu response Rasa
        FE-->>U: Hien thi tung phan
        API->>DB: Luu bot response + source=Rasa
    else Rasa fallback hoac confidence thap
        API-->>FE: Event routing=RAG
        API->>RAG: Generate answer(question, conversation context)
        RAG->>Emb: Tao embedding cho question
        Emb-->>RAG: Query vector
        RAG->>VDB: Similarity search topK
        VDB-->>RAG: Chunks + metadata + score
        RAG->>RAG: Loc nguong, rerank, tao prompt
        alt Khong co chunk dat nguong
            RAG-->>API: Fallback answer / yeu cau hoi lai
            API-->>FE: Stream fallback message
        else Co ngu canh phu hop
            RAG->>LLM: Prompt gom question + context + policy
            loop LLM streaming tokens
                LLM-->>RAG: Token
                RAG-->>API: Token + citation metadata
                API-->>FE: SSE/WebSocket chunk
                FE-->>U: Cap nhat cau tra loi
            end
            RAG-->>API: Done + citations
        end
        API->>DB: Luu bot response + source=RAG + citations
    end
